In Rhode Island, is a so

15
00:00:37,330 --> 00:00:39,180
called opt-in state.

16
00:00:39,180 --> 00:00:42,740
In our case, the opt-in is very strict.

17
00:00:42,740 --> 00:00:48,100
As an HIE, we cannot even see your
data until you have given consent for

18
00:00:48,100 --> 00:00:50,220
