generate a proper CCD,

63
00:03:24,780 --> 00:03:29,780
attach it to a direct message, and send
it to the current care gateway where,

64
00:03:29,780 --> 00:03:33,750
it is checked to see whether that
patient has consented or not, and

65
00:03:33,750 --> 00:03:37,100
