70
00:03:46,790 --> 00:03:47,480
>> Very much so.

71
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:49,300
In fact, it's automatic.

72
00:03:49,300 --> 00:03:54,150
Once it's set up, when the provider
takes a certain action like lockup

73
